n hoà ước thành cảm tác - 壬戌年和約成感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-6pamu7FlLkIevS5S6C9yfw">Nguyễn Ngọc Tương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/Nhi%E1%BB%87t-H%E1%BA%A3i-h%C3%A0nh-t%E1%BB%91ng-Th%C3%B4i-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-ho%C3%A0n-kinh/poem-7PKSPJiR7OpVcwgxW92kiA">Nhiệt Hải hành tống Thôi thị ngự hoàn kinh - 熱海行送崔侍御還京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/author-AcWs16LhWAEAw513Kk2DnA">Sầm Tham</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Ti%E1%BB%85n-m%C3%B4n-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-Ngh%C4%A9a-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-L%C3%AA-Nh%C6%B0-B%E1%BA%A1ch-nh%C3%A2n-k%C3%BD-kinh-th%C3%A0nh-ch%C6%B0-m%C3%B4n-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-1tn74y6UOln4mkQPJ-8Yag">Tiễn môn đệ Nghĩa Định sứ quân Lê Như Bạch, nhân ký kinh thành chư môn đệ kỳ 2 - 餞門弟義定使君黎如白，因寄京城諸門弟其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C4%83ng-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Phi%C3%AAn/Tu%E1%BA%BF-m%E1%BB%99-t%E1%BA%A1p-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-cUyPj_K6Rwyjkr42IUTBIw">Tuế mộ tạp cảm - 歲暮雜感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C4%83ng-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Phi%C3%AAn/author-nwGIjF6JjQC812vXoHUn9A">Tăng Quốc Phiên</a>)<br></div>	</div>
